      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Mixing St. John's Wort with sertraline is not recommended, as it can cause a serious interaction that leads to serotonin syndrome, which is a dangerous condition. You should absolutely not try this combination. Instead, focus on getting more sleep and maybe a quick, intense workout to boost your energy. For immediate mood support, try a very low dose of Vitamin B complex and remember that a little stress is totally normal during finals.",
