    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it says it's a risk but like, i've read that it's mostly just an issue if you take massive amounts? i'm only thinking about doing a pretty small dose, like maybe just once a day to get through the week. surely a little bit won't cause anything crazy like that? it's just a plant after all.",
