    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the caffeine and magnesium sounds okay but i'm still kinda hesitant about the sertraline/st johns wort thing. i just feel like everyone says natural stuff is way safer for your body than meds. if i take the st johns wort in the morning and my sertraline at night, wouldn't that be fine? like, they aren't really in my system at the same time so the interaction wouldn't happen, right?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
