      "content": "The timing doesn't negate the chemical interaction; the compounds still compete for serotonin receptors, so it's still a risk, no matter the schedule. You should treat this as a high-risk maneuver, and for the sake of your mental health, skip the herbal supplement entirely. Instead, try a strong dose of L-Theanine with your morning coffee to get that focused energy without the chemical interference.",
